timeline.body:
a better name is `addQueries` as that matches the `addPaths` we already have.
To make it more efficient it should do:
```java
if (StringUtil.isEmpty(query1))
  return query2;
if (StringUtil.isEmpty(query2))
  return query1;
return query1 + '&' + query2;
```

